snippet.title: Total War: WARHAMMER 2 - The Prophet & The Warlock Trailer [PEGI ENG]
snippet.description:
Total War: WARHAMMER II’s latest Lords Pack, The Prophet & The Warlock. Cackling rat-men with rotary cannons? Check. Sinuous Salamanders with scorching spittle? Check.

Get the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/965220/
